---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="LogisticsEdge privacy policy — how we handle your data.">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="page-header" style="background: none; padding: 3rem 0 1rem;">
      <h1 class="page-header__title" style="color: var(--color-navy);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-header__description" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Last updated: 6 April 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        LogisticsEdge (<a href="https://logisticsedge.co.uk">logisticsedge.co.uk</a>) is a UK-based
        logistics and customs information resource. Our contact email is
        <a href="mailto:hello@logisticsedge.co.uk">hello@logisticsedge.co.uk</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What data we collect</h2>
      <h3>Newsletter subscribers</h3>
      <p>
        If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. This is processed by
        <a href="https://buttondown.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Buttondown</a>,
        our email service provider. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email.
      </p>

      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This collects anonymised
        data including pages visited, time on site, and approximate location (country level). No
        personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.
      </p>

      <h3>Advertising</h3>
      <p>
        We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based
        on your prior visits to this or other websites. You can opt out of personalised advertising
        by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google Ad Settings</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site uses the following types of cookies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — Required for basic site functionality.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — Help us understand how visitors use the site (Google Analytics). Only set with your consent.</li>
        <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong> — Used by Google AdSense to serve relevant ads. Only set with your consent.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can manage your cookie preferences at any time using the cookie settings on this site,
        or through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK data protection law (UK GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, email us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@logisticsedge.co.uk">hello@logisticsedge.co.uk</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        Newsletter subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe. Analytics data is retained
        for 14 months as per Google Analytics default settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> — Site hosting and CDN</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — Website analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — Advertising</li>
        <li><strong>Buttondown</strong> — Email newsletter</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page
        shows when it was last revised.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions about this privacy policy or your data, email
        <a href="mailto:hello@logisticsedge.co.uk">hello@logisticsedge.co.uk</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
